# Petory UI Design

Full spec: [docs/UI-DESIGN.md](../../docs/UI-DESIGN.md)

## Three Surfaces

| Surface | Path | Tone |
|---------|------|------|
| **Client panels** | `src/renderer/` | Warm soft minimal, companion app |
| **Admin console** | `server/admin/public/` | Same tokens, sidebar nav, denser tables OK |
| **Marketing site** | `website/` | Hero + features + download; user-facing copy only |

## Client Colors (Tailwind `petory-*`)

- Primary `#FF8A7A` · Bg `#FAFAF8` · Surface `#FFFFFF` · Text `#2D2A26`
- One Primary per action group; use `components/ui/Button`, not raw `<button>`

## Admin Layout (required)

- **Sidebar + single view** — never stack all modules on one scroll page
- Views: overview · users · devices · commerce · generation · logs · config
- Lazy-load API per view; topbar: refresh + logout

## Website Copy

- No `npm run`, env vars, yml/json paths, or API names in user-visible HTML
- Match MVP features; dev details stay in `docs/`

## Key Client Components

`Button` · `TextButton` · `Pill` · `PanelHeader` · `Input` · `PageShell`

## Don't

Corporate dashboard on **client**; neon chrome; expose API names in user UI; demo/dev copy on website; admin single-page dump; multiple primary buttons; raw styled buttons in renderer.
